Set 1 km from the Marrakesh train station, this relaxed hotel in a peach building is 2 km from Majorelle Garden and 4 km from the bustling Jemaa el-Fnaa market square.

    About this hotel

    Set 1 km from the Marrakesh train station, this relaxed hotel in a peach building is 2 km from Majorelle Garden and 4 km from the bustling Jemaa el-Fnaa market square. …

    Bright rooms feature free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and dining areas, as well as en suite bathrooms. Some offer balconies with city views. Apartments sleep to 4 guests and add separate living rooms, kitchenettes, and balconies with pool views.

    Amenities include an outdoor pool with sunloungers, and a poolside cafe. Breakfast is available (fee).
